<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Roboto:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/products-cart.css">
  <link href="css/header.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/footer.css">
  <title>Mi carrito de compras</title>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <div class="home-caja-suprema">
        <div class="home-caja1">
            <img src="img/logo.png" alt="logo en proceso">
            <div class="home-caja2">
                <h1>SANWI</h1>
                <p>Los mejores sandwiches del pueblo</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="home-menu-hamburguesa-no-tan-hamburguesa">
            <i class="fas fa-th-list"></i>
        </div>
        <div class="home-caja3">
            <div class="home-form">
                <form action="/" method="post">
                    <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                    <input type="search" placeholder="Lomitos, Hamburguesas, Milanesas, etc.." name="buscador" id="buscador">
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <nav>
        <ul>
            <li>
                <a href="/">Inicio</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="product-detail">Productos</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="login">Iniciar Sesión</a>
            </li>
            <li>
                <a href="register">Registro</a>
            </li>
        </ul>
        <div class="home-carrito">
            <i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i>
            <i class="fas fa-sort-down"></i>
        </div>
    </nav>
</header>
  <main class="products-cart__container">
    <h1 class="products-cart__title">Carrito de compra</h1>
    <a href="#" class="products-cart__link">Seguir comprando</a>
    <form>
      <table class="products-cart__table">
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Producto</th>
            <th>Cantidad</th>
            <th>Precio</th>
            <th>Total</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="products-cart__product">
              <a href="#" class="products-cart__product-detail-image">
                <img class="products-cart__thumbnail-image" src="/img/tostado-de-jamon-y-queso.avif"
                  alt="tostado de jamón y queso">
              </a>
              <div class="products-cart__product-container">
                <a href="#" class="products-cart__product-detail-name">
                  <p class="products-cart__product-name">Tostado de jamón y queso</p>
                </a>
                <p class="products-cart__product-description">Guarnición: Sin guarnición</p>
                <button class="products-cart__product-remove">Quitar</button>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td>
              <input type="number" name="quantity" max="20" min="1" value="1" id="quantity">
            </td>
            <td>
              <span>$2.300</span>
              <div>
                <label for="quantity">Cantidad</label>
                <input type="number" name="quantity" max="20" min="1" value="1" id="quantity">
              </div>
            </td>
            <td>$2.300</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="products-cart__product">
              <a href="#" class="products-cart__product-detail-image">
                <img class="products-cart__thumbnail-image" src="/img/sandwich-de-jamon-crudo-y-burrata.webp"
                  alt="tostado de jamón y queso">
              </a>
              <div class="products-cart__product-container">
                <a href="#" class="products-cart__product-detail-name">
                  <p class="products-cart__product-name">Sándwich de jamón crudo y burrata</p>
                </a>
                <p class="products-cart__product-description">Guarnición: Papas fritas</p>
                <button class="products-cart__product-remove">Quitar</button>
              </div>
            </td>
            <td>
              <input type="number" name="quantity" max="20" min="1" value="1" id="quantity">
            </td>
            <td>
              <span>$4.800</span>
              <div>
                <label for="quantity">Cantidad</label>
                <input type="number" name="quantity" max="20" min="1" value="1" id="quantity">
              </div>
            </td>
            <td>$4.800</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <div>
        <div>
          <label class="products-cart__date-of-delivery-or-takeout" for="date-of-delivery/takeout">¿Fecha de
            delivery/takeout?</label>
          <span class="products-cart__datepicker-toggle">
            <span class="products-cart__datepicker-toggle-button"></span>
            <input type="date" min="2023-07-26">
          </span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="note" class="products-cart__note">¿Querés agregar una nota a tu pedido? ¿Querés enviar un mensaje
            de regalo?</label>
          <textarea name="note" id="note" rows="3"></textarea>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="products-cart__subtotal">
        <p>Subtotal</p>
        <span>$7.100 ARS</span>
      </div>
      <p>Impuestos incluidos. <a href="#">Revisá acá los gastos de envío</a> que se agregarán en la pantalla de pagos.
      </p>
      <button type="button">Continuar</button>
    </form>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>Copyright © 2023-2023 Sanwi</p>
    </footer>
</body>

</html>